 Contact Me 

 Please feel free to contact me if you have any questions. 

 If you run into something that you think might be a bug, please send me the error log file, the output file from the job, and a detailed description of the behavior. I treat all information confidentially. 

 For answers to common questions, please see the  Frequently Asked Questions . 

 You can also view and ask questions on  Stack Exchange . When you ask questions, remember to add the tag ola-hallengren. 

 Do you have an idea for a new feature? Please send it to me. Many of the features in the SQL Server Maintenance Solution come from ideas from users